      "parameters": {
        "width": 700,
        "height": 240,
        "content": "### üé• From Video Upload to Blog Prompt\n\nThis part of the workflow starts when a new video is added to a designated Google Drive folder. It downloads the video and converts it into base64 format. That base64 video is then sent to Dumpling AI‚Äôs `extract-video` endpoint, which transcribes the entire audio content. The transcription is passed to GPT-4o, which writes a full blog post and also creates a descriptive image prompt based on the video's message.\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "8a379ab7-b7ba-409f-a072-c3e0c7e20f7e",
